ew 16:17–18, Christ says more explicitly, ‘Blessed art thou, Simon Bar-jona … thou art Peter, and upon this rock I will build my church’. The name has been in continuous use since the Middle Ages."],"variants":[]}],"historicEvents":[{"id":1357045,"age":2,"year":"1054","julianDay":2106026,"description":"Sweden and Denmark set boundaries.","jurisdictionLevel":0},{"id":1702072,"age":48,"year":"1100","julianDay":2122827,"title":"Vreta Abbey is First Christian Convent","description":"Vreta Abbey was established around 1100 and was the first Christian convent in Sweden. It was located in modern-day Linkoping Municipality. It was founded on orders of Pope Paschal II with large donations by King Inge the Elder and Queen Helena.","jurisdictionLevel":0}],"lifeSummary":"Mrs Peder Kjeldsen Thott was born about 1052, in Sweden. She had at least 1 son with Peter Kjeldsen Thott I."},"et":{"Abt 1052–":"umbes 1052–Surnud","1050–Male":"1050–Surnud","1104–Male":"1104–Surnud","1052–Female":"1052–Surnud","abt 1104":"umbes 1104","Abt 1052":"umbes 1052","1104":"1104","1100":"1100","1054":"1054","1052":"1052","1050":"1050","Löddeköpinge, Harjager, Malmöhus, Sweden":"Löddeköpinge, Harjager, Malmöhus, Rootsi","Loddekoping,sweden":"Rootsi"},"fi":{"Abt 1052–":"noin 1052–Kuollut","1050–Male":"1050–Kuollut","1104–Male":"1104–Kuollut","1052–Female":"1052–Kuollut","abt 1104":"noin 1104","Abt 1052":"noin 1052","1104":"1104","1100":"1100","1054":"1054","1052":"1052","1050":"1050","Löddeköpinge, Harjager, Malmöhus, Sweden":"Löddeköpinge, Harjager, Malmöhus, Ruotsi","Loddekoping,sweden":"Ruotsi"},"fr":{"Abt 1052–":"environ 1052–Décédée","1050–Male":"1050–Décédé","1104–Male":"1104–Décédé","1052–Female":"1052–Décédée","abt 1104":"environ 1104","Abt 1052":"environ 1052","1104":"1104","1100":"1100","1054":"1054","1052":"1052","1050":"1050","Löddeköpinge, Harjager, Malmöhus, Sweden":"Löddeköpinge, Harjager, Malmöhus, Suède","Loddekoping,sweden":"Suède","lifeSummary":"Mrs Peder Kjeldsen Thott est née enviro